{"tid":1723960,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[正視聽] 休息撚入","createTime":"2019-11-15T10:36:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T13:52:47.000Z","uid":13099,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"2971ada9894e471477b02a228fb470e7ead287f2","tid":1723960,"uid":13099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T10:36:27.000Z","msg":"前線都未撚出聲話休息 你班撚屌衝曬出嚟幫前線被休息做乜鳩？對上一次休息 一抖抖咗2個星期 唔係多得政府同狗出嚟火水救火 場運動一早輸咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係得香港人革命先話會休息<br />\n<br />\n簡單嚟講休息後果：<br />\n1. 俾狗有兩日休息機會 重新部署 同埋專心查案 上門拉手足<br />\n2. 一鼓作氣 再而休 三而竭<br />\n3. 啱啱先有返少少革命氣氛 講就講話休息兩日 對上一次休息一日 再下次聚得返啲人 已經係兩星期嘅事<br />\n<br />\n黎明行動可以停星期六日 但唔係休息 革命係唔可以休息<br />\n希望大家唔好再俾再亂宣布休息 <br />\n<br />\n你地諗下俾人拉咗嘅手足有冇得休息 每日被自殺嘅手足點諗"},{"pid":"2524b5d2b58be229bd62c46ff807d088ae16aa98","tid":1723960,"uid":292624,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T10:37:32.000Z","msg":"星期六日係和你shop回氣唔係休息<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5abe39b9fc7fbbedcf1f4b61f136d693b4f31a99","tid":1723960,"uid":144996,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T10:39:01.000Z","msg":"冇錯<br />\n而家係背水一戰 士氣嘅嘢好難再聚"},{"pid":"88cc4107a10e74f4351a44a17a84842b4036bd90","tid":1723960,"uid":13099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T10:43:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"80ed92c4399b4b62e53e641bd27c099beca1db98","tid":1723960,"uid":13099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T10:43:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"85f54dfad2f0d3093a9fb4acf480b7a6ba4420f9","tid":1723960,"uid":13099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T10:43:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ec71432115a0e6ae430eab2b4a30e05bcac9dcf5","tid":1723960,"uid":13099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T10:43:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8d5ce5fe4a13a6b8cea5ea6c1323dfea1b61eba8","tid":1723960,"uid":13099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy